  <entry>
    <title>A Morning on the Trail</title>
    <link href="https://fadyfahim.com/adventures/trips/first-hike/"/>
    <updated>2026-04-01T00:00:00Z</updated>
    <id>https://fadyfahim.com/adventures/trips/first-hike/</id>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;There&#39;s something special about getting out early before the rest of the world wakes up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;The Trail&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Started at dawn, about 6 AM. The air was crisp and the trail was empty. Just me and the sounds of the forest waking up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Highlights&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spotted some deer near the creek&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Great views from the ridge&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Made it back before lunch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Stats&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Distance&lt;/strong&gt;: 8 miles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Elevation gain&lt;/strong&gt;: 1,200 ft&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Time&lt;/strong&gt;: 4 hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;photo-gallery&quot;&gt;
  &lt;figure class=&quot;gallery-item&quot;&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;https://fadyfahim.com/assets/images/placeholder-trail.jpg&quot; class=&quot;lightbox-link&quot; data-caption=&quot;Morning light on the trail&quot;&gt;
      &lt;img src=&quot;https://fadyfahim.com/assets/images/placeholder-trail.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Sunlight filtering through trees on a forest trail&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Morning light on the trail&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Already planning the next one.&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
